OL,3,CThe Tories said they'll cut migration
OL,4,C- but haven't they promised that
OL,5,Cbefore?
OL,7,FITV News Political Correspondent
OL,8,FRomilly Weeks looks at the
OL,9,FConservative promises on migration
OL,10,Fover the years, and the pledges of the
OL,11,Fother parties.
OL,13,FFor the past 14 years successive
OL,14,FConservative governments have pledged
OL,15,Fto cut net migration, while the
OL,16,Foverall number has continued to rise.
