OL,3,CThe Tories said they'll cut migration
OL,4,C- but haven't they promised that
OL,5,Cbefore?
OL,7,FNet migration is the difference
OL,8,Fbetween the number of people coming in
OL,9,Fto the country, and the number
OL,10,Fleaving. It hit a record high of
OL,11,F745,000 in 2022, and despite falling
OL,12,Fby 10% in 2023 to 685,000 - the number
OL,13,Fremains three times higher than in
OL,14,F2019.
OL,16,FRishi Sunak has joined his
OL,17,Fpredecessors in saying he wants the
OL,18,Ffigure to come down, committing on
OL,19,FTuesday to what he calls an
OL,20,F'Immigration Lock' - an annual cap on
OL,21,Fwork and family visas.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/11
