OL,3,CThe Tories said they'll cut migration
OL,4,C- but haven't they promised that
OL,5,Cbefore?
OL,7,FHe says the cap will reduce every year
OL,8,Ffor the five years of the next
OL,9,Fparliament, but crucially he hasn't
OL,10,Fcommitted to a number he'd like to get
OL,11,Fit down to.
OL,13,FInstead, MPs would vote each year on
OL,14,Freducing the numbers, which would be
OL,15,Fbased on recommendations from the
OL,16,FMigration Advisory Committee (MAC).
