OL,3,CThe Tories said they'll cut migration
OL,4,C- but haven't they promised that
OL,5,Cbefore?
OL,7,FNow Foreign Secretary David Cameron
OL,8,Fwas the first person who promised to
OL,9,Fcut the numbers back when he was Tory
OL,10,Fleader during the 2010 election,
OL,11,Fsaying he'd get net migration down to
OL,12,F"tens of thousands." At that point it
OL,13,Fstood at 252,000.
OL,15,FIn 2011 he doubled down on this,
OL,16,Fsaying he would hit the target by 2015
OL,17,F- "no ifs, no buts." When the 2015
OL,18,Felection rolled around, net migration
OL,19,Fhad risen to 379,000.
