OL,3,CThe Tories said they'll cut migration
OL,4,C- but haven't they promised that
OL,5,Cbefore?
OL,7,FWhen Boris Johnson became leader, he
OL,8,Frefused to commit to a specific
OL,9,Ffigure, but promised "overall numbers
OL,10,Fwould come down". At the end of 2019
OL,11,Fnet migration was 274,000 - and the
OL,12,Fnumbers have kept going up.
OL,14,FThe prime minister is hoping his new
OL,15,Fpromise to cut net migration will
OL,16,Fincrease pressure on Labour.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G6/11
