OL,3,CThe Tories said they'll cut migration
OL,4,C- but haven't they promised that
OL,5,Cbefore?
OL,7,FLabour leader Sir Keir Starmer has
OL,8,Falso committed to bring down migration
OL,9,Flevels, telling the Sun newspaper -
OL,10,F"read my lips - I will cut
OL,11,Fimmigration." But he's also refused to
OL,12,Fset an overall target, committing
OL,13,Finstead to training more UK workers in
OL,14,Fareas where there are skills shortages.
OL,16,FOn the other hand, the Reform Party -
OL,17,Fnewly led by Nigel Farage - say the UK
OL,18,Fshould aim for zero net migration,
OL,19,Fonly allowed skilled workers into the
OL,20,FUK in strictly limited numbers.
