OL,3,CThe Tories said they'll cut migration
OL,4,C- but haven't they promised that
OL,5,Cbefore?
OL,7,FThe Liberal Democrats say they don't
OL,8,Fwant to set targets, but would give
OL,9,Fvisas to those who benefit the UK
OL,10,Feconomy, and also train more British
OL,11,Fworkers. They say this would make net
OL,12,Fmigration figures fall.
OL,14,FIn Scotland, the SNP want more inward
OL,15,Fmigration to plug workforce and skills
OL,16,Fgaps.
