OL,3,CThe Tories said they'll cut migration
OL,4,C- but haven't they promised that
OL,5,Cbefore?
OL,7,FOverall a total of 802,000 visas to
OL,8,Fwork or study in the UK were issued
OL,9,Flast year. The government has already
OL,10,Fbrought in some measures to try and
OL,11,Fbring that figure down.
OL,13,FLast year they announced they would
OL,14,Fincrease the salary threshold for
OL,15,Fskilled workers to #38,700, a nearly
OL,16,F50% rise on the previous figure which
OL,17,Fwas a minimum of #26,200.
OL,19,FThey have also banned most students
OL,20,Ffrom bringing family members over with
OL,21,Fthem.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G9/11
