OL,3,CThe Tories said they'll cut migration
OL,4,C- but haven't they promised that
OL,5,Cbefore?
OL,7,FGovernment figures suggest those
OL,8,Fmeasures are starting to have an
OL,9,Fimpact with visa applications for
OL,10,Fhealth and care workers down 50%, and
OL,11,Fthose for students down 60% in the
OL,12,Ffirst few months of 2024. But,
OL,13,Fapplications for skilled worker visas
OL,14,Fhave increased by 50%.
OL,16,FBut there are economic trade-offs,
OL,17,Fwith universities heavily reliant on
OL,18,Fthe income from overseas students, and
OL,19,Fthe care sector particularly
OL,20,Fstruggling with labour shortages.
